distraction: I was not. I was focusing on just this :)
strategies: I did not use any strategies; just relied on my memory but also my understanding of what AI images look land feel like.
familiar: If it felt like I'd something I'd seen before - anywhere. IRL or over the internet. If it felt like places I'd visited it was rated as highly familiar.
memorable: If I remembered places like it or whether I'd remember seeing the image because of its distinctiveness.
unique: Whether the location or the focus on the image was a structure of some kind (natural or man-made) that looked like it was one of a kind.
realistic: AI image vs whether it was a photograph.
similar: I have not participated in a similar study on another platform.
comments: This was just the right length for a study like this.
